title: Carnegie Institution of Washington Publication
additional-note: This is a monographic series.  Before concluding an issue is in the public domain, search for renewals for an issue under its distinctive title. We have not systematically checked issue titles for this serial. The renewal record for the portion of number 376 mentioned here is the first active renewal record to specifically mention the Carnegie Institution of Washington. It appears in the Books section of the CCE, not the Periodical section.
